cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

The paper deals with the automated detection of masses in mammograms using deep learning techniques. This falls under the domain of computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The use of transfer learning and SVM classifiers also suggests the involvement of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and multimedia (cs.MM) subcategories. Additionally, the use of extensive experiments to investigate the robustness of the classifiers suggests the involvement of neural networks (cs.NE) subcategory.
